text: Hermias Strauss (born 4 June 1997) is a Namibian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Namibia in the 2016–17 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge on 15 January 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Namibian cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Windhoek
